    "headline": "Introducing Oceania Aurelia™, The Ultimate Explorer",
    "summary": "Oceania Cruises®, the world's leading culinary- and destination-focused luxury cruise line, today unveiled Oceania Aurelia™, The Ultimate Explorer, purposefully designed for extended global discoveries. Debuting in late 2027, she will be the ideal home at sea for long, immersive journeys, including the line's 2028 and 2029 Around the World voyages as well as a series of expansive Grand Voyages.",
